In the street there is an earnestness, enthusiasm, motion a blur, little kid running very fast with legs and tradition black hat but he jumps up the stairs and inside and i stare at him and cannot possibly fix the sensation, cannot possibly feel his feeling in my legs, but i look at the little kid the place where the little kid just was but now that place is just fall leaves on concrete, the beautiful concrete texture with the lines that go down between slabs to make picture perfect compositions every time, just take the right angles, and think: "haha, it me", i wish that were me there running.
